<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>274</hymn_number>
<title>SINCE JESUS COME INTO MY HEART</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka hinna ah kithenna maktak ahung um,
 Ka lunga Isu hung apat!
 Hun sawttak a ka hawl, lungthim ah vak ka nei,
 Ka lunga Isu hung apat!

[V2]
 Ka lunga Isu hung apat,
 Ka lunga Isu hung apat!
 Ka lunggil kipahna tuipi luonggi a bang,
 Ka lunga Isu hung apat!

[V3]
 2. Ka vakmangna leh chieh khelhna ka haihsan tai,
 Ka lunga Isu hung apat!
 Ka gitlohna tamtak chuh sawpthien ahi tai,
 Ka lunga Isu hung apat.

[V4]
 3. Taksanna det leh zuou ngeilo chu ka nei tai,
 Ka lunga Isu hung apat;
 Ginlahna meipi thimin ka lam khuh lo ding,
 Ka lunga Isu hung apat!

[V5]
 4. Thihna luiguom ah tun kei di'n vakna a um,
 Ka lunga Isu hung apat;
 Chunglam a Khawpi kulh kawtkhakte ka mu thei,
 Ka lunga Isu hung apat.

[V6]
 5. Khawpi achun cheng di'n chieh ingka tih ka he'i,
 Ka lunga Isu hung apat;
 Malam zuonin kipak takin ka chieh zel hi,
 Ka lunga Isu hung apat.</lyrics>
</song>